data.description: Exquisite Luxurious Tuscan Villa overlooking the 5th TeeBox w/beautiful Views of the Golf Course, Mountains and Las Vegas Strip. TIMELESS European architecture meets elegant custom interior design & highest quality. Living room boasts soaring ceilings appointed w/Gorgeous Restoration Hardware Designer Chandeliers. Beautiful Travertine & Hardwood flooring. Entertain in style in Formal Dining room that opens to Custom-Built Home Theater w/high-def Surround Sounds & oversized projection screen TV. Spiraling Mahogany Staircase compliments the 20 feet high ceilings. 2nd level showcasing custom-built Library, 2 guest beds & Den. Large Primary Suite invites you to relax while viewing sunsets & sparkling City Lights. Corner lot with no neighbors on the side. Tuscany is a Guard gated secured Community w/array of amenities,Clubhouse, Golf, Tennis,Swimming Pool/Spa,Restaurant,Bar, Fitness Center. This Home exudes sophistication & opulent style with unparalleled comfort & beauty. INCREDIBLE VALUE!
